  stimulus_text = 'The article discusses the process of "decolonizing" a museum''s collection of artifacts.  The process is described as complex and challenging, and the writer notes that the process is "ongoing."  What is the most likely reason why the writer uses the word "ongoing"? Taken together, these details imply a broader principle that extends beyond the immediate example, though the author stops short of claiming universal proof. Readers must weigh both the evidence presented and the limits the author acknowledges.',
